# Project Structure

This React portfolio/personal website is built with Vite, TypeScript, Material-UI, and Jotai for state management.

## Technology Stack

- **Framework**: React 19.X with TypeScript
- **Build Tool**: Vite 7.X
- **UI Library**: Material-UI (MUI) 7.X
- **State Management**: Jotai 2.X
- **Routing**: React Router DOM 7.X
- **Testing**: Vitest 4.X + @testing-library/react
- **Linting**: ESLint 9.X
- **Styling**: Emotion (@emotion/react, @emotion/styled)

